                             sessionUdr.request
                            - original HTTP requestm needed to respond back to the client and preserve headers/tagId/context
                            
                            sessionUdr.requestObj
                            - decoded client business request, needed to build RFC/S4 requests
                            
                            sessionUdr.responseObj
                            - client response being built, then at the end when we return back to client we will set originalRequest.someField equal to this final response object
