/*
============================================================================
Analysis_Request Agent

This agent handles request preparation for the /history and /withdraw endpoints.

This agent handles these transaction lifecycle stages:

1. RFC_REQUEST
   - For /history, builds the RFC request

2. RFC_RESPONSE
   - For /history, receives the RFC response and validates the returned
     CA and BP

3. ODATA_REQUEST
   - For /history, builds the S4 GET request used to retrieve Promise To Pay
     history.
   - For /withdraw, builds the first S4 GET request used to fetch the CSRF
     token/header before the actual withdraw POST.

4. RESPONSE
   - Handles early validation or RFC error responses before the request reaches
     Analysis_Response.
============================================================================
*/


